{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/environmentvalues\/isluminancereduced"]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues\/isLuminanceReduced","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isLuminanceReduced"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When you detect this condition, lower the overall brightness of your view.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, you can change large, filled shapes to be stroked, and choose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"less bright colors:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["@Environment(\\.isLuminanceReduced) var isLuminanceReduced","","var body: some View {","    if isLuminanceReduced {","        Circle()","            .stroke(Color.gray, lineWidth: 10)","    } else {","        Circle()","            .fill(Color.white)","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition to the changes that you make, the system could also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dim the display to achieve a suitable brightness. By reacting to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isLuminanceReduced"},{"text":", you can preserve contrast and readability","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"while helping to satisfy the reduced brightness requirement.","type":"text"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On watchOS, the system typically sets this value to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"text":" when the user","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"lowers their wrist, but the display remains on. Starting in watchOS 8, the system keeps your","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view visible on wrist down by default. If you want the system to blur the screen","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"instead, as it did in earlier versions of watchOS, set the value for the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/bundleresources\/information-property-list\/wksupportsalwaysondisplay","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"key in your app’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/bundleresources\/information-property-list","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"file to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that indicates whether the display or environment currently requires"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reduced luminance."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/EnvironmentValues"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUICore\/Data\/Environment\/LuminanceReduced.swift#L47","fileName":"LuminanceReduced.swift"},"role":"symbol","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"introducedAt":"10.15","name":"ma